  35     class BuildGuard
  36     {
  37         public nothrow BuildGuard(MainWindow* mainWindow_) : mainWindow(mainWindow_)
  38         {
  39             mainWindow->SaveBackendConfig();
  40             mainWindow->SetControlStatus(UserInterfaceAction.build);
  41         }
  42         public ~BuildGuard()
  43         {
  44             mainWindow->SetControlStatus(UserInterfaceAction.none);
  45             mainWindow->RestoreBackendConfig();
  46         }
  47         private MainWindow* mainWindow;
  48     }
  49 
  50     class DebugGuard
  51     {
  52         public nothrow DebugGuard(MainWindow* mainWindow_) : mainWindow(mainWindow_), startFailed(false)
  53         {
  54             mainWindow->SaveBackendConfig();
  55             mainWindow->SetControlStatus(UserInterfaceAction.debug);
  56             mainWindow->ResetDebugLocation();
  57             mainWindow->SetTargetStopped(false);
  58         }
  59         public nothrow void SetStartFailed()
  60         {
  61             startFailed = true;
  62         }
  63         public ~DebugGuard()
  64         {
  65             if (startFailed)
  66             {
  67                 mainWindow->SetControlStatus(UserInterfaceAction.none);
  68             }
  69             else
  70             {
  71                 mainWindow->SetControlStatus(UserInterfaceAction.debugging);
  72             }
  73             mainWindow->RestoreBackendConfig();
  74             mainWindow->SetTargetStopped(true);
  75         }
  76         private MainWindow* mainWindow;
  77         private bool startFailed;
  78     }

 111     public SourceSpan GetSourceSpan(const Location& loc)
 112     {
 113         int line = 0;
 114         short scol = 0;
 115         short ecol = 0;
 116         if (!loc.line.IsEmpty())
 117         {
 118             line = ParseInt(loc.line);
 119         }
 120         if (!loc.scol.IsEmpty())
 121         {
 122             scol = ParseShort(loc.scol);
 123         }
 124         if (!loc.ecol.IsEmpty())
 125         {
 126             ecol = ParseShort(loc.ecol);
 127         }
 128         SourceSpan span(line, scol, ecol);
 129         return span;
 130     }

 132     public string GetCmajorProjectsDirectory()
 133     {
 134         const char* cmajorRootEnv = RtGetEnvironmentVariable("CMAJOR_ROOT");
 135         if (cmajorRootEnv != null)
 136         {
 137             string cmajorRoot = GetFullPath(cmajorRootEnv);
 138             return Path.Combine(cmajorRoot, "projects");
 139         }
 140         else
 141         {
 142             return string();
 143         }
 144     }

 146     public string Title()
 147     {
 148         return "Cmajor Code - " + System.ToString(WinGetCurrentProcessId());
 149     }

 585         protected override void OnWindowClosing(bool& cancelClose)
 586         {
 587             try
 588             {
 589                 if (!buildService.IsNull())
 590                 {
 591                     buildService->Quit();
 592                     buildService.Reset();
 593                 }
 594                 if (!debugService.IsNull())
 595                 {
 596                     debugService->Stop();
 597                     debugService.Reset();
 598                 }
 599                 CloseSolutionClick();
 600                 Application.SetLogView(null);
 601                 Cm.Views.Bitmaps.Instance().Clear();
 602                 base->OnWindowClosing(cancelClose);
 603                 MainConfiguration.Instance().Save(true);
 604             }
 605             catch (const Exception& ex)
 606             {
 607                 MessageBox.Show(ex.Message());
 608                 LogException(ex);
 609             }
 610         }

 724         private void CodeTabPageSelected()
 725         {

 727             Cm.Views.Editor* editor = GetEditorByTabPage(selectedTabPage);
 728             if (editor != null)
 729             {
 730                 gotoLineMenuItem->Enable();

 732                 editor->Select();

 734                 if (textView != null)
 735                 {
 736                     if (!textView->IsSelectionEmpty())
 737                     {
 738                         copyMenuItem->Enable();
 739                         cutMenuItem->Enable();
 740                     }
 741                     else
 742                     {
 743                         copyMenuItem->Disable();
 744                         cutMenuItem->Disable();
 745                     }
 746                 }
 747             }
 748         }
 749         private void CodeTabPageRemoved(ControlEventArgs& args)
 750         {
 751             Control* removedControl = args.control;
 752             if (removedControl is TabPage*)
 753             {
 754                 TabPage* removedTabPage = cast<TabPage*>(removedControl);
 755                 Cm.Views.Editor* editor = GetEditorByTabPage(removedTabPage);
 756                 if (editor != null)
 757                 {
 758                     if (editor->IsDirty())
 759                     {
 760                         MessageBoxResult result = MessageBox.Show(editor->FilePath() + " is modified. Save changes?", "Question", this, MessageBoxType.MB_YESNO);
 761                         if (result == MessageBoxResult.yes)
 762                         {
 763                             editor->Save();
 764                         }
 765                     }
 766                 }
 767                 editorByTabPageMap.Remove(removedTabPage);
 768                 if (removedTabPage == debugTabPage)
 769                 {
 770                     debugTabPage = null;
 771                 }
 772             }
 773             if (codeTabControl->TabPages().IsEmpty())
 774             {
 775                 sourceFilePathStatusBarItem->SetText("");
 776             }
 777         }
 778         private void OutputTabControlTabPageRemoved(ControlEventArgs& args)
 779         {

 841         private void TreeViewNodeClick(TreeViewNodeMouseClickEventArgs& args)
 842         {
 843             try
 844             {
 845                 TreeViewNode* node = args.node;
 846                 if (args.buttons == MouseButtons.rbutton)
 847                 {
 848                     TreeViewNodeData* data = cast<TreeViewNodeData*>(node->Data());
 849                     if (data->kind == TreeViewNodeData.Kind.solution)
 850                     {
 851                         UniquePtr<ContextMenu> contextMenu(new ContextMenu());
 852                         MenuItem* addNewProjectMenuItem = new MenuItem("Add New Project...");
 853                         contextMenu->AddMenuItemAction(addNewProjectMenuItem, new AddNewProjectAction(this, solution.Get()));
 854                         MenuItem* addExistingProjectMenuItem = new MenuItem("Add Existing Project...");
 855                         contextMenu->AddMenuItemAction(addExistingProjectMenuItem, new AddExistingProjectAction(this, solution.Get()));
 856                         MenuItem* buildMenuItem = new MenuItem("Build");
 857                         contextMenu->AddMenuItemAction(buildMenuItem, new BuildSolutionAction(this, solution.Get()));
 858                         MenuItem* rebuildMenuItem = new MenuItem("Rebuild");
 859                         contextMenu->AddMenuItemAction(rebuildMenuItem, new RebuildSolutionAction(this, solution.Get()));
 860                         MenuItem* cleanMenuItem = new MenuItem("Clean");
 861                         contextMenu->AddMenuItemAction(cleanMenuItem, new CleanSolutionAction(this, solution.Get()));
 862                         MenuItem* openFileLocationMenuItem = new MenuItem("Open File Location");
 863                         contextMenu->AddMenuItemAction(openFileLocationMenuItem, new OpenFileLocationAction(this, solution->FilePath()));
 864                         if (contextMenu->HasMenuItems())
 865                         {
 866                             Point loc = args.location;
 867                             Point screenLoc = solutionExplorerTreeView->ClientToScreen(loc);
 868                             ShowContextMenu(contextMenu.Release(), screenLoc);
 869                         }
 870                     }
 871                     else if (data->kind == TreeViewNodeData.Kind.project)
 872                     {
 873                         Cm.Ast.Project* project = data->project;
 874                         UniquePtr<ContextMenu> contextMenu(new ContextMenu());
 875                         if (solution->ActiveProject() != project)
 876                         {
 877                             MenuItem* setActiveMenuItem = new MenuItem("Set Active");
 878                             contextMenu->AddMenuItemAction(setActiveMenuItem, new SetActiveProjectAction(this, solutionExplorerTreeView, solutionExplorerData.Get(), 
 879                                 solution.Get(), project, node));
 880                         }
 881                         MenuItem* addNewSourceFileMenuItem = new MenuItem("Add New Source File...");
 882                         contextMenu->AddMenuItemAction(addNewSourceFileMenuItem, new AddNewSourceFileAction(this, project, node));
 883                         MenuItem* addExistingSourceFileMenuItem = new MenuItem("Add Existing Source File...");
 884                         contextMenu->AddMenuItemAction(addExistingSourceFileMenuItem, new AddExistingSourceFileAction(this, project, node));

2874         private void Search(SearchExtent extent, const List<string>& files, const List<ustring>& lines, const string& searchText, bool wholeWords, bool caseInsensitive, bool regularExpression)
2875         {
2876             Cm.Views.SearchResults* searchResults = GetSearchResults();
2877             searchResults->Clear();
2878             ustring text = ToUtf32(searchText);
2879             if (caseInsensitive)
2880             {
2881                 text = ToLower(text);
2882             }
2883             Nfa* re = null;
2884             Context context;
2885             Nfa nfa;
2886             if (regularExpression)
2887             {
2888                 nfa = CompileRegularExpressionPattern(context, u".*(" + text + u").*");
2889                 re = &nfa;
2890             }
2891             for (const string& fileName : files)
2892             {
2893                 List<ustring> readLines;
2894                 List<ustring>* lns = &readLines;
2895                 if (extent == SearchExtent.currentFile)
2896                 {
2897                     lns = &lines;
2898                 }
2899                 else
2900                 {
2901                     List<string> utf8Lines = File.ReadAllLines(fileName);
2902                     for (const string& utf8Line : utf8Lines)
2903                     {
2904                         readLines.Add(ToUtf32(utf8Line));
2905                     }
2906                 }
2907                 long n = lns->Count();
2908                 for (long i = 0; i < n; ++i;)
2909                 {
2910                     ustring* line = &(*lns)[i];
2911                     ustring lowerLine;
2912                     if (caseInsensitive)
2913                     {
2914                         lowerLine = ToLower(*line);
2915                         line = &lowerLine;
2916                     }
2917                     if (Search(*line, text, wholeWords, re))
2918                     {
2919                         searchResults->Add(new Cm.Views.SearchResult(fileName, i + 1, ToUtf8((*lns)[i])));
2920                     }
2921                 }
2922             }
2923             searchResults->Invalidate();
2924         }
2925         private bool Search(const ustring& line, const ustring& text, bool wholeWords, Nfa* re)
2926         {
2927             if (re != null)
2928             {
2929                 return Match(*re, line);
2930             }
2931             else
2932             {
2933                 long pos = line.Find(text);
2934                 while (pos != -1)
2935                 {
2936                     bool match = true;
2937                     if (wholeWords)
2938                     {
2939                         if (pos > 0)
2940                         {
2941                             uchar prev = line[pos - 1];
2942                             if (IsAlphabetic(prev) || IsNumber(prev))
2943                             {
2944                                 match = false;
2945                             }
2946                         }
2947                         if (pos + text.Length() < line.Length())
2948                         {
2949                             uchar next = line[pos + text.Length()];
2950                             if (IsAlphabetic(next) || IsNumber(next))
2951                             {
2952                                 match = false;
2953                             }
2954                         }
2955                     }
2956                     if (match)
2957                     {
2958                         return true;
2959                     }
2960                     pos = line.Find(text, pos + 1);
2961                 }
2962             }
2963             return false;
2964         }
